snippet.title: Secrets of Magic - The Book of Spells - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
An evil witch has kidnapped Victoria’s parents and now it’s up to her going after them. But first Victoria needs to learn the fine art of magic. Dive into a magical world of witches and wizards. Travel through magical lands and help Victoria to collect unique items along her journey to become a witch. Leam from the ancient Book of Spells in this engaging Match-3 game.

And prove your skills in the Challenge mode!!!

Features:
+ Tons of unique and challenging Match-3 levels.
+ A rich and vibrant world.
+ Collect coins to upgrade your power-ups.
+ Top your high scores and get all the stars.
